<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189596>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Phylogeny based on maximum likelihood analysis of 379 bp of the mitochondrial COI gene. Search involved 10 random addition replicates using a GTR + I + G model. Branches are proportional to substitutions per site (scale indicated). Bold names indicate species described in this study. M. = Myrsidea." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189596/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

